content:
Deploy Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking by assigning permissions, enabling CRM Analytics, and creating and sharing the analytics app for your users.

Enable CRM Analytics in Salesforce before you create an app from the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking template.

Assign relevant permissions to admin and users to manage the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking app.

Set Field-Level Security to Analytics Integration User profile has access to all of the fields that the app uses.

Requirements for Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking Data: Ensure data meets specific requirements or the data fails the CRM Analytics check.

Embed Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking Dashboard from Lightning Experience pages.

Create and Share the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking App by creating an app from the template and sharing with users.

Keep the Data in the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking App Up-to-Date by scheduling regular refreshes.
title: Deploying CRM Analytics for Order Tracking
